    "# Anytime Try Scorer Probability Model\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook builds a machine learning model to predict the probability of any player scoring a try in an NRL match.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Features Used:\n",
    "- Player historical try scoring rate\n",
    "- Team attack/defense metrics\n",
    "- Home/Away advantage\n",
    "- Match context (opponent, round, form)"
